      .main-content__first-column
        p.main-content__first-column-text
         | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
         | Donec leo nisi, feugiat vel placerat vitae, vulputate ac nibh.
         | Ut scelerisque quis nulla sed tempor.

        .main-content__first-column-nav
          .main-content__nav-prev
          .main-content__nav-next.main-content__nav-next--disabled

      .main-content__second-column
          h4.main-content__title Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur

          p.main-content__second-column__text
            | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec
